WEBVTT

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Sareena Chaudry-Masan an ITP major, talks about how she wanted to get the Sierra Madre or Yosemite dorms the most because they align with her social values.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Her favourite items in her dorm are the pictures she has of her family, and she looks at them whenever she misses them.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:31.000
She is able to make the most of her small space by sharing a lot of things with her roommate instead of having unnecessary duplicates.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Encourages incoming freshman to research each of the living communities on campus because it can go a long way in determining where they end up. 

00:00:49.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Shares that her favourite thing about dorm living is being surrounded by people and never feeling alone at college.